사이킷런 Estimator Class¶

1. 라이브러리/모듈 import¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.datasets import load_boston

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')

2. 데이터 셋 로딩¶

In [ ]:
boston = load_boston()
X_data =  boston.data
y_target = boston.target

boston

type(X_data)
In [ ]:
type(y_target)

bostonDF = pd.DataFrame(X_data, columns = boston.feature_names)
In [ ]:
bostonDF['PRICE'] = boston.target

3. 시각화를 위해 feature는 RM만 추출,target은 price로 추출¶

In [ ]:
X_feature = bostonDF['RM'].values.reshape(-1,1) 
#  feature , 1
In [ ]:
X_feature

4. x_test 데이터를 임의로 4.5 ~ 8.5 까지 100개 데이터 셋 생성¶

  • rm
  • prediction ( test )
  • np.arrange(start, stop, step) #start stop-1 step array
  • range(start, stop, step)
In [ ]:
X_test = np.arange(4.5, 8.5, 0.04).reshape(-1, 1)   #4.5 8.5 0.04  100-->1
In [ ]:
print(X_test)

5. 회귀트리(DecisionTreeRegressor)를 이용, 학습/예측¶

5.1) 회귀트리 모듈 import¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.tree import DecisionTreeRegressor

5.2) DecisionTreeRegressor의 max_depth=2, 학습/예측¶

In [ ]:
rf_reg2 = DecisionTreeRegressor(max_depth=2)
In [ ]:
rf_reg2.fit(X_feature, y_target)
In [ ]:
pred_rf2 = rf_reg2.predict(X_test)

5.3) DecisionTreeRegressor의 max_depth=7, 학습/예측¶

In [ ]:
rf_reg7 = DecisionTreeRegressor(max_depth=7)
In [ ]:
rf_reg7.fit(X_feature, y_target)
In [ ]:
pred_rf7 = rf_reg7.predict(X_test)

5.4) Linear Regression을 이용 학습/예측¶

In [ ]:
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression
In [ ]:
lr_reg = LinearRegression()
In [ ]:
lr_reg.fit(X_feature, y_target)
In [ ]:
pred_lr = lr_reg.predict(X_test)

6. 결과 시각화¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns

6.1)선형 회귀로 학습된 모델의 회귀 예측선¶

In [ ]:
plt.title('Linear Regression')
plt.scatter(x=bostonDF['RM'], y=bostonDF['PRICE'], c="darkorange")
plt.plot(X_test, pred_lr,label="linear", linewidth=2)
plt.show()

6.2)DecisionTreeRegressor의 max_depth=2로 학습된 모델의 회귀 예측선¶

In [ ]:
plt.title('Decision Tree Regression: \n max_depth=2')
plt.scatter(x=bostonDF.RM, y=bostonDF.PRICE, c="darkorange")
plt.plot(X_test, pred_rf2, label="max_depth:2", linewidth=2 )
plt.show()

6.3)DecisionTreeRegressor의 max_depth=7로 학습된 모델의 회귀 예측선¶

In [ ]:
plt.title('Decision Tree Regression: \n max_depth=7')
plt.scatter(x=bostonDF.RM, y=bostonDF.PRICE, c="darkorange")
plt.plot(X_test, pred_rf7, label="max_depth:7", linewidth=2)
plt.show()

6.4)subplot으로 세 그림을 한꺼번에 출력¶

In [ ]:
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

fig, (ax1, ax2, ax3) = plt.subplots(figsize=(14,4), ncols=3)

# X 4.5 ~ 8.5   ,        
#       
ax1.set_title('Linear Regression')
ax1.scatter(x=bostonDF.RM, y=bostonDF.PRICE, c="darkorange")
ax1.plot(X_test, pred_lr,label="linear", linewidth=2, c="darkorange")

# DecisionTreeRegressor max_depth 2     
ax2.set_title('Decision Tree Regression: \n max_depth=2')
ax2.scatter(x=bostonDF.RM, y=bostonDF.PRICE, c="darkorange")
ax2.plot(X_test, pred_rf2, label="max_depth:2", linewidth=2 )

# DecisionTreeRegressor max_depth 7     
ax3.set_title('Decision Tree Regression: \n max_depth=7')
ax3.scatter(x=bostonDF.RM, y=bostonDF.PRICE, c="darkorange")
ax3.plot(X_test, pred_rf7, label="max_depth:7", linewidth=2)

plt.show()
